<main class="recipe-content">
  <img src="../images/pancakes.jpg" alt="Fluffy Pancakes" class="recipe-img">
  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>1 cup flour</li>
    <li>2 tbsp sugar</li>
    <li>1 cup milk</li>
    <li>1 egg</li>
    <li>1 tsp baking powder</li>
    <li>Pinch of salt</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Instructions</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Mix dry ingredients in a bowl.</li>
    <li>Whisk milk and egg, then combine with dry mix.</li>
    <li>Heat pan and pour batter to form pancakes.</li>
    <li>Cook until golden brown on both sides.</li>
  </ol>
</
